node.text:
I‘m not just the typical BEAUTIFUL BODY, there is more, Soooooo much MORE. Most people know me from what I show them here on my social media accounts with all the perfect pics. But the real Nadine Kerastas is more than this. I partnered with @prominentstatus_ic to show you my whole story behind them and my life as an full time influencer and model. Listen to me while I explain the difference from being a bikini competitor & a full time influencer in the pursuit of building my own brand. Don’t watch me, WATCH ME‼️😄😘
Prominent Status....Full Video and episode coming soon.
. .

Prod | @aduanegvisual 
Apparel | @prmnt782887 
Mua | @lauraariasmua 
Photog | @10kphotographyy | @crzypanda
mPowered by | @prominentstatus_ic 
Campaign | Prominent Status Experience

node.title: WHO IS NADINE KERASTAS?! | wATcH ME
